1
00:00:03,010 --> 00:00:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop grinning at me like 
that while eating.</font>

2
00:00:06,390 --> 00:00:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help it. It's good.</font>

3
00:00:11,030 --> 00:00:12,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

4
00:00:12,750 --> 00:00:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

5
00:00:14,610 --> 00:00:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always make a scary face, Syugo.</font>

6
00:00:18,050 --> 00:00:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so shocked 
when you jumped at Kizuki.</font>

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen you make 
a face like that before.</font>

8
00:00:26,130 --> 00:00:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a chef, what will you do 
if you hurt your hand?</font>

9
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you out of your mind?</font>

10
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Kizuki!</font>

11
00:00:33,390 --> 00:00:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throwing hands at each other like that—</font>

12
00:00:36,430 --> 00:00:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more talking about Kizuki.</font>

13
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:46,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

14
00:00:46,650 --> 00:00:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now...</font>

15
00:00:47,990 --> 00:00:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person in front of you...</font>

16
00:00:52,260 --> 00:00:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is me.</font>

17
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Out of anyone else, 
the one by your side...</font>

18
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is me.</font>

19
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2030</font></font>

20
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apartment's small, 
but make yourself at home.</font>

21
00:03:07,790 --> 00:03:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

22
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck were you and Syugo 
doing in front of Mizuho?</font>

23
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I wanted to be 
the one to lay it on you.</font>

24
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You abandoned Mizuho for three years.</font>

25
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

26
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idiot.</font>

27
00:03:45,970 --> 00:03:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one you need 
to apologize to is Mizuho.</font>

28
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask you something?</font>

29
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you break up with Mizuho?</font>

30
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ran away.</font>

31
00:04:14,610 --> 00:04:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2021</font></font>

32
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget him.</font>

33
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's forget about Kizuki.</font>

34
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet everyone else thinks so too, right?</font>

35
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough, Kai.</font>

36
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Kizuki's our friend.</font>

37
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate that part about adults.</font>

38
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kai-kun. Everyone...</font>

39
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry.</font>

40
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#dbeff8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

41
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><font color="#92b0cb">Start Again from Respawn Area</font></font></font></font>

42
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f2f5f6">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

43
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><font color="#92b0cb">Return to Title</font></font></font></font>

44
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over!</font>

45
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot!</font>

46
00:04:45,970 --> 00:04:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were so close to finishing that!</font>

47
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're useless! You held me back!</font>

48
00:04:50,410 --> 00:04:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're no friend, Kizuki!</font>

49
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When are we <i>ever</i> going to 
defeat the dragon at this rate?!</font>

50
00:04:58,830 --> 00:05:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys...</font>

51
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long are you going to play games?</font>

52
00:05:02,010 --> 00:05:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about making plans for Kizuki's birthday?</font>

53
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is Kizuki even here?!</font>

54
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a mess!</font>

55
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now.</font>

56
00:05:10,890 --> 00:05:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You play the game 
for us instead, Shin-chan.</font>

57
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come back after I take a bath.</font>

58
00:05:15,490 --> 00:05:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to bed!</font>

59
00:05:19,210 --> 00:05:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kai's angry.</font>

60
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mizuho.</font>

61
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How should I have used this item?</font>

62
00:05:28,870 --> 00:05:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm cramping from laughing so much.</font>

63
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your timing was completely off.</font>

64
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho.</font>

65
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let me see. For that item...</font>

66
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to go home.</font>

67
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

68
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost midnight.</font>

69
00:05:39,460 --> 00:05:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I told my dad.</font>

70
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be in the room of a guy</font>

71
00:05:43,850 --> 00:05:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who isn't your boyfriend 
this late at night.</font>

72
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're right.</font>

73
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll head home soon, then.</font>

74
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki. Go drop her off.</font>

75
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Okay.</font>

76
00:05:55,110 --> 00:05:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for having me over.</font>

77
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of an honor student.</font>

78
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No "I'll take you home" 
or anything like that?</font>

79
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking, Shin-chan?</font>

80
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? It's common sense.</font>

81
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leaving those two alone 
on a day like this...</font>

82
00:06:13,850 --> 00:06:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to pretend 
that you're fine.</font>

83
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?!</font>

84
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You surprised me!</font>

85
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since it's going to be 
tomorrow in ten minutes...</font>

86
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to give you one last kiss 
while I'm still 16.</font>

87
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki.</font>

88
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything you want 
for your birthday?</font>

89
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing, really.</font>

90
00:07:02,650 --> 00:07:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's something I want to know.</font>

91
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about me made you like me, Mizuho?</font>

92
00:07:10,030 --> 00:07:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, well...</font>

93
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is so sudden.</font>

94
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

95
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wha—?</font>

96
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's take the scenic route.</font>

97
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not going home until you tell me!</font>

98
00:07:32,180 --> 00:07:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a ton of things I like 
about you, Mizuho.</font>

99
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

100
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you chase your 
dreams of writing manga.</font>

101
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How you cheer me on when I'm swimming.</font>

102
00:07:44,850 --> 00:07:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How your hair is a mess because 
you're too tired in the mornings.</font>

103
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

104
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you dissing me in the last one?</font>

105
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I...</font>

106
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like about you...</font>

107
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why it had to be you...</font>

108
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't think of a word 
that perfectly describes that.</font>

109
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

110
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hope."</font>

111
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since we were kids...</font>

112
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the hardships, you never 
gave up and swam towards your dreams.</font>

113
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a ray of hope to me.</font>

114
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I leave it at that?</font>

115
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was the time I thought to myself...</i></font>

116
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I'll continue to swim 
for Mizuho no matter what."</i></font>

117
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted to continue 
being her ray of hope.</i></font>

118
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's past midnight now.</font>

119
00:08:58,350 --> 00:09:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was your first kiss as a 17 year old.</font>

120
00:09:01,010 --> 00:09:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy Birthday, Kizuki.</font>

121
00:09:05,110 --> 00:09:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really did think that.</i></font>

122
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. From our first year in high school.</font>

123
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah, the inter-high preliminaries.</font>

124
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so frustrated that 
I placed 3rd on that day.</font>

125
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You also accidentally wore 
your senpai's sandals, right?</font>

126
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you even record that?</font>

127
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you practicing too much, Kizuki?</font>

128
00:09:35,010 --> 00:09:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The virus finally calmed down, so new 
matches could start up again this season.</font>

129
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

130
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my last chance.</font>

131
00:09:45,610 --> 00:09:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want Mizuho to see me swim 
at the inter-high finals.</font>

132
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:03,920
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#636970">{\an9}Kanto High School Championship</font>

133
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:03,920
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#636970"><b>{\an7}Swimming Competition</b></font>

134
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:01,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now for the 52nd program.</i></font>

135
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Boys 100 meter freestyle final.</i></font>

136
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In Lane 6,</i></font>

137
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}3rd year Kizuki Hazawa 
from Aogasaki High School.</i></font>

138
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki! Give it your all!</font>

139
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gotta win and make the inter-highs!</font>

140
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a bold declaration of victory.</font>

141
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's unstoppable.</font>

142
00:10:35,530 --> 00:10:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His eyes are totally just on Mizuho.</font>

143
00:10:38,830 --> 00:10:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Take your marks!</i></font>

144
00:10:44,470 --> 00:10:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then...</i></font>

145
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was enveloped in a blue light.</i></font>

146
00:10:51,590 --> 00:10:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt like I was able to go 
anywhere within that light.</i></font>

147
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#d0ad8c">Boys         100 Meter                     Freestyle                       Finals</font></b></font></font>

148
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#bc9576">1st  Kizuki Hazawa           Aogasaki</font></b></font></font>

149
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2022</font></font>

150
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kizuki?</font>

151
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get that?</font>

152
00:11:16,090 --> 00:11:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup! I did.</font>

153
00:11:18,620 --> 00:11:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be sure to come back home during 
the Koigahama Fireworks Festival.</font>

154
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We absolutely have to go together.</font>

155
00:11:26,370 --> 00:11:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is it?</font>

156
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You miss me because I got into college 
and live in the dorms now, right?</font>

157
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh! I can visit you 
whenever I want to!</font>

158
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not that far away!</font>

159
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cute, Mizuho!</font>

160
00:11:40,700 --> 00:11:42,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop teasing me!</font>

161
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font color="#f4f0f0">2025</font></font></font>

162
00:11:55,530 --> 00:11:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We somehow made it.</font>

163
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so glad we made it just in time.</font>

164
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Mizuho's job searching now?</font>

165
00:12:03,330 --> 00:12:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

166
00:12:04,410 --> 00:12:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she had an interview today, too.</font>

167
00:12:06,370 --> 00:12:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's applied to 20 or 30 places by now.</font>

168
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you, Kizuki?</font>

169
00:12:11,470 --> 00:12:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll go to graduate school
for sports science next year.</font>

170
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still disappointed that I couldn't 
make the Japanese national team</font>

171
00:12:19,130 --> 00:12:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">at last year's championships...</font>

172
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to see how much 
I can push my skills</font>

173
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and fight against all 
those amazing people</font>

174
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with such high levels 
of effort and talent.</font>

175
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You make me so mad with how cool you are.</font>

176
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch.</font>

177
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no good at all.</font>

178
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hazawa's generation hasn't improved.</font>

179
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the kids after that 
are getting stronger.</font>

180
00:12:55,890 --> 00:12:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be because 
they missed out on practice?</font>

181
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are the pandemic generation, after all.</font>

182
00:13:00,990 --> 00:13:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That crucial time when they could gain 
the most experience as a player</font>

183
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is practically a blank slate, yeah.</font>

184
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your eyes used to 
light up so much about it.</font>

185
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think you'd quit swimming...</font>

186
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I panicked.</font>

187
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Kizuki!</font>

188
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm telling you this as your doctor!</font>

189
00:13:40,380 --> 00:13:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been practicing 
without permission, haven't you?!</font>

190
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your shoulder's not 
in good shape right now!</font>

191
00:13:45,890 --> 00:13:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand you're in a rush 
to improve your results.</font>

192
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But overworking will take 
a toll on your life!</font>

193
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know about my body better 
than anyone else.</i></font>

194
00:13:58,950 --> 00:14:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gather around!</font>

195
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's Kizuki?</font>

196
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

197
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The usual goodies.</font>

198
00:14:15,550 --> 00:14:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

199
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it easy.</font>

200
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have plans with Chika, 
so I need to go now.</font>

201
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck on your practice!</font>

202
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

203
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost the qualifying match!</font>

204
00:14:28,050 --> 00:14:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been waiting for this day forever.</font>

205
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you'll do amazing!</font>

206
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm rooting for you!</font>

207
00:14:34,690 --> 00:14:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

208
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best for you, Mizuho.</font>

209
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's no good at all.</i></font>

210
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hazawa's generation hasn't improved.</i></font>

211
