<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That crucial time when they could gain 
the most experience as a player</i></font>

215
00:14:56,590 --> 00:14:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><font color="#ffffff">is practically a blank slate, yeah.</font></i></font>

216
00:15:09,890 --> 00:15:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do I do?</font>

217
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need immediate surgery.</font>

218
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I undergo surgery,</font>

219
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">wouldn't that mean 
I won't be able to swim for a while?</font>

220
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly.</font>

221
00:15:22,610 --> 00:15:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what about the qualifying match?</font>

222
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, you're going to 
have to sit this one out.</font>

223
00:15:28,110 --> 00:15:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, you need to rest 
and think about recovering your body.</font>

224
00:15:32,490 --> 00:15:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait!</font>

225
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just the qualifying match.</font>

226
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the next season?</font>

227
00:15:38,530 --> 00:15:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When would I recover?!</font>

228
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I <i>can</i> go back to normal, right?!</font>

229
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but I can't make any promises.</font>

230
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you don't do anything, 
you're going to stay like this.</font>

231
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please...</font>

232
