<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Arial"><font color="#3f3e42">Rehabilitation Center</font></font></b></font>

233
00:16:02,230 --> 00:16:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it, Kizuki.</font>

234
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it still hurt?</font>

235
00:16:14,890 --> 00:16:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm fine.</font>

236
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's try three more.</font>

237
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

238
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki.</font>

239
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't rush, okay?</font>

240
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it slow.</font>

241
