<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#c6d1d9">Kizuki Hazawa (Athlete)</font></font></font></font>

244
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#c6d1d9">Taichi Aida (Athlete)</font></font></font></font>

245
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now for sports.</i></font>

246
00:16:40,060 --> 00:16:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Some bad news for Kizuki Hazawa, who 
has been gaining attention in swimming.</i></font>

247
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Due to a previously 
reported shoulder injury,</i></font>

248
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it was announced that he will miss 
all remaining events this season.</i></font>

249
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}At this time, there is 
no confirmed date for his return.</i></font>

250
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

251
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What I...</font>

252
00:16:59,830 --> 00:17:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like about you...</font>

253
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why it had to be you...</font>

254
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't think of a word 
that perfectly describes that.</font>

255
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

256
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Hope."</font>

257
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since we were kids...</font>

258
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter the hardships, you never 
gave up and swam towards your dreams.</font>

259
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a ray of hope to me.</font>

260
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I leave it at that?</font>

261
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't be Mizuho's ray of hope.</i></font>

262
00:17:57,620 --> 00:17:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You quit the swim team?!</font>

263
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you had surgery. You went to rehab.</font>

264
00:18:03,210 --> 00:18:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've worked so hard!</font>

265
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:09,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And your shoulder was 
getting better little by little.</font>

266
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was all pointless.</font>

267
00:18:12,460 --> 00:18:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not pointless!</font>

268
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you don't really want to quit!</font>

269
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't decide that for me.</font>

270
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:19,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you giving up?!</font>

271
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

272
00:18:23,320 --> 00:18:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gave up your dreams to write manga 
and ended up an office worker.</font>

273
00:18:32,690 --> 00:18:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to give up.</font>

274
00:18:34,380 --> 00:18:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep going.</font>

275
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it gets hard and you want to cry,</font>

276
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll wipe your tears away for you.</font>

277
00:18:53,300 --> 00:18:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I decided to start job searching.</font>

278
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

279
00:18:57,570 --> 00:19:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm starting so late that
 I'm worried I won't even get to be</font>

280
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a normal office worker.</font>

281
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Mizuho...</font>

282
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay with that?</font>

283
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

284
00:19:08,370 --> 00:19:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can just read manga as a side hobby.</font>

285
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to chase your dreams 
in my stead, Kizuki.</font>

286
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't I finally give up, too?</font>

287
00:19:23,650 --> 00:19:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

288
00:19:25,770 --> 00:19:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a kid anymore.</font>

289
00:19:27,980 --> 00:19:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm tired of foolishly chasing dreams.</font>

290
00:19:32,800 --> 00:19:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not a kid anymore, yeah. But...</font>

291
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then.</font>

292
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

293
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about us?</font>

294
00:20:02,810 --> 00:20:04,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That day...</font>

295
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hurt Mizuho...</font>

296
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and ran away.</font>

297
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2030</font></font>

298
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Then I got a job. 
Cut off contact with you all.</font>

299
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And tried to forget everything.</font>

300
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

301
00:20:24,990 --> 00:20:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just couldn't forget 
about swimming and Mizuho.</font>

302
00:20:30,460 --> 00:20:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, I'm still 
that timid younger brother.</font>

303
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki. It's okay.</font>

304
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I brought this up.</font>

305
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must have been hard for you.</font>

306
00:20:56,730 --> 00:21:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found this where you 
and Syugo were fighting.</font>

307
00:21:00,270 --> 00:21:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This old keychain...</font>

308
00:21:02,870 --> 00:21:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long have you held onto this?</font>

309
00:21:05,330 --> 00:21:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw this and immediately figured it out.</font>

310
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That your feelings for Mizuho 
haven't changed at all.</font>

311
00:21:14,530 --> 00:21:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the youngest.</font>

312
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do things at your own pace.</font>

313
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a weakling.</font>

314
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too honest for your own good.</font>

315
00:21:28,020 --> 00:21:30,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="28" color="#526779"><b>{\an7}Graduation
<font size="16">Koigahama Municipal Elementary School</font></b></font>

316
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew that you only had eyes 
for Mizuho for a long time, Kizuki.</font>

317
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because Mizuho's 
always been looking my way.</font>

318
00:21:46,600 --> 00:21:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even when I was weak with my asthma,</font>

319
00:21:49,150 --> 00:21:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or when I couldn't improve my time,</font>

320
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or when my soul was crushed...</font>

321
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She made me stronger 
when I was at my weakest.</font>

322
00:21:58,190 --> 00:22:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">That's why I'm so happy that 
my feelings were able to reach her!</font></font>

323
00:22:03,010 --> 00:22:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were always looking straight forward.</font>

324
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I loved about you.</font>

325
00:22:12,700 --> 00:22:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

326
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Airu...</font>

327
00:22:16,580 --> 00:22:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand up, Kizuki.</font>

328
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you still love Mizuho,</font>

329
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you need to take a stand once more.</font>

330
00:24:01,210 --> 00:24:03,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you still love Mizuho,</i></font>

331
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:08,050
